{"tid":2041523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為了抗議梁君彥驅逐朱凱廸離場 泛民議員今日以標語紙牌代替真人出席會議","createTime":"2020-05-29T09:41:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T10:11:11.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cb9586dd340032bff8ad1e0183b4ca88b0fbc5ef","tid":2041523,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T09:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o6hQOBc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo6hQOBc.jpg&h=7eb47513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨日的立法會国歌法二讀，梁君彥指朱凱廸展示的「最佳主席李慧琼」標語帶侮辱成份，而驅逐朱凱廸離場。<br />\n<br />\n建制派與立法會保安聯手奪權成為主席的李慧琼今日主持內會，民主派杯葛「不合法」的會議，豎起「最佳主席李慧琼」標語並拒絕出席會議。<br />\n<br />\n雖然泛民議員都不在席，但建就連標語都沒法接受。民建聯葛珮帆提出規程問題，指標語與議程無關，要求處理；李慧琼立即應葛的要求，命保安移除標語。<br />\n<br />\n會議在只有一種聲音下，無人提問、無人要求跟進，極速處理了16項議程。<br />\n<br />\n#自治全失<br />\n【奪權李慧琼掌內會 泛民豎「最佳主席」杯葛拒出席】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2TSfIQF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2TSfIQF&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33CKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=faa4dfde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2TSfIQF</a><br />\n【民政專員聞「國家安全」即離席 觀塘區議會通過反對國安法】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2zykgEZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zykgEZ&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33CKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=6afc1edd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2zykgEZ</a><br />\n=============<br />\n🍎 黎智英：經營非常困難 請支持訂閱<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2VLuV6g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2VLuV6g&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33CKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=4887fc07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2VLuV6g</a><br />\n=============<br />\n😷 全民自救 即睇武漢肺炎專頁<br />\n緊貼疫情最新消息：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2V8fypM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2V8fypM&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33CKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=e4c14117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2V8fypM</a><br />\n=============<br />\n📣 召集有心人！贊助學生免費睇